nodes.text: Lew'el, which meant deluge, was an aquatic planet located in the galaxy. Originally settled by humans a long time ago, Lew'el remained a largely forgotten world by those who craved power. Humans native to Lew'el were called Lew'elans.
Lew'el was where Luke Skywalker learned to spearfish, something that would help him survive during his time on Ahch-To.
